Package xyz.model

Class User

java.lang.Object
org.json.JSONObject
xyz.model.ModelObject
xyz.model.User
public class User
extends ModelObject
User model used by framework to identify user sessions and login with passsword. UID key is the email for users and users should be associated with GroupID for access priveleges
